    """DTW constrained by Itakura Parallelogram

    :Parameters:
       x : 1d array_like object (N)
          first sequence
       y : 1d array_like object (M)
          second sequence
       dist_only : bool
          compute only the distance
       metric : 'euclidean', 'sqeuclidean' or 'cosine'
