    .. [Itakura75] F Itakura. Minimum prediction residual principle applied to speech recognition. Acoustics, Speech and Signal Processing, IEEE Transactions on, 23(1), 67â€“72, 1975. doi:10.1109/TASSP.1975.1162641.
